  <name>CloudToLocalLLM</name>
  <summary>Bridge cloud-based AI services with local AI models</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      CloudToLocalLLM is a cross-platform application that bridges cloud-based AI services 
      with local AI models, providing a hybrid AI architecture with privacy-first design.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Seamlessly switch between cloud AI (OpenAI, Anthropic) and local models (Ollama)</li>
      <li>Privacy-first: sensitive data stays local while leveraging cloud AI when needed</li>
      <li>Secure tunneling for real-time communication</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support for Windows, Linux, and Web</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
